long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly export Houzz professionals search listing data.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Open an Houzz professionals search listing page.
2️⃣ Click open our extension, then click the Export button.
3️⃣ Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

🔥 Key Features:
1️⃣ Run in the background without waiting for finish.
2️⃣ Export on multiple listing pages simultaneous.
3️⃣ Export professionals listing data for current item to Excel or CSV file, data include:  User Id, Zip Code, State, Review Rating, Pro Type Name, Review numbers,Location, Highlight Badges, Has Verified KYC, Has Verified License, Phone, Country, City,Budget Levels,Address, About Me  etcs.

🎯 Targeted Users: business owners, data analysts, and competitor researchers alike.

💡 Benefit from our dedicated support team! We're here to assist you at every step and provide prompt, knowledgeable help.

💪 Take control of your business data management and make informed decisions with Houzz Professionals Exporter today!

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Houzz ❗️🔒
